{"tid":926762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何志平突放棄自辯 料周二結案陳詞","createTime":"2018-12-03T16:29:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T03:05:40.000Z","uid":51183,"like":132,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"bb5bbc15176cca6666705bba8bf7c9e46bd8801d","tid":926762,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T16:29:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181204/58989016\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181204%2F58989016&d=mjxy7jgeiAJDqMaDnlkTCjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=cffd262d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181204%2F58989016&h=e7a4debc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181204/58989016</a><br />\n<br />\n前民政事務局長何志平涉賄賂非洲官員案，踏入第6日聆訊。不過在聆訊開始前，何志平突然表示，決定不出庭作供自辯。法官隨即指出，根據美國憲法，他有自辯的權利，並詢問何志平是否主動放棄該權利，何志平確認。根據法官較早前預計，案件仍需3日才會進入結案陳詞階段，但法官現表示，預計最快美國時間星期二，就能結案陳詞。<br />\n<br />\n在前5日聆訊，庭上的供詞已對何志平相當不利，包括指出何志平很可能以聯合國，作為行賄的途徑，接觸各國政要，並為中國華信尋找生意機會，最後亦涉以200萬美元，賄賂乍得總統。而案中非常重要的中間人、前塞內加爾外長加迪奧，亦與政府達成不檢控協議（non-prosecution agreement），並轉為污點證人，指證何志平。有律師接受《蘋果》訪問時估計，何被定罪的機會極大。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都係美國監獄安全好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb8aeae01c24fb15136d0979d9c93d78107a1f3","tid":926762,"uid":36178,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T16:31:36.000Z","msg":"放棄自己屙屎"},{"pid":"034738b26c1c5ca89a8fc67f00fa29974d352922","tid":926762,"uid":35656,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T16:31:53.000Z","msg":"可以慢慢享用黑腸了"},{"pid":"f2f7a40c6b644a96f0929d8c0b6e418443bb7da8","tid":926762,"uid":125300,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T16:32:08.000Z","msg":"命仔緊要, 戲都廢事做.."},{"pid":"e4edd60d0ab1ebccbf64229dd0d47a9383009864","tid":926762,"uid":155818,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"ci